WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 19=

00:01:44.700 --> 00:01:45.540 line:80%
Milady.

00:01:45.730 --> 00:01:47.980 line:80%
Did Mr. Chang upset you?.

00:01:50.060 --> 00:01:50.900 line:80%
No.

00:01:51.420 --> 00:01:52.260 line:80%
Don't mention him.

00:01:55.730 --> 00:01:56.900 line:80%
Something feels off.

00:01:59.290 --> 00:02:00.540 line:80%
Alright, I'm tired.

00:02:00.540 --> 00:02:01.380 line:80%
Gonna sleep.

00:02:05.290 --> 00:02:06.900 line:80%
Something's off. Something's off.

00:02:08.490 --> 00:02:09.620 line:80%
Something's off.

00:02:11.300 --> 00:02:12.380 line:80%
(Carefree)

00:02:12.380 --> 00:02:13.260 line:80%
When

00:02:13.650 --> 00:02:14.970 line:80%
the Young Master arrives later,

00:02:15.530 --> 00:02:16.930 line:80%
everyone smile.

00:02:16.930 --> 00:02:18.140 line:80%
Make it cheerful

00:02:18.140 --> 00:02:19.000 line:80%
and sweet.

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:20.340 line:80%
Make our Young Master

00:02:20.340 --> 00:02:22.060 line:80%
so happy

00:02:22.060 --> 00:02:24.020 line:80%
he's over the moon.

00:02:24.020 --> 00:02:25.410 line:80%
Make him so happy

00:02:25.410 --> 00:02:27.020 line:80%
he's over the moon.

00:02:27.020 --> 00:02:27.860 line:80%
Smile.

00:02:29.180 --> 00:02:30.860 line:80%
Master You, if you're tired of living,

00:02:31.300 --> 00:02:32.180 line:80%
just say so.

00:02:33.300 --> 00:02:34.140 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:02:34.460 --> 00:02:35.490 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:02:36.020 --> 00:02:37.020 line:80%
Mr. Mu, calm down.

00:02:37.020 --> 00:02:38.140 line:80%
Elder Yan said

00:02:38.140 --> 00:02:39.580 line:80%
you've been working hard.

00:02:39.580 --> 00:02:41.060 line:80%
It's unwise to be without a maid.

00:02:41.060 --> 00:02:42.060 line:80%
We picked some

00:02:42.060 --> 00:02:43.900 line:80%
cheerful girls.

00:02:43.900 --> 00:02:44.900 line:80%
Mr. Mu, just choose one.

00:02:48.530 --> 00:02:49.370 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:02:49.860 --> 00:02:51.780 line:80%
I'm from Qinglong Altar.

00:02:51.780 --> 00:02:53.370 line:80%
Long heard of your fame.

00:02:53.370 --> 00:02:54.780 line:80%
Seeing you today,

00:02:54.780 --> 00:02:57.090 line:80%
a poem popped into my head.

00:02:57.090 --> 00:02:58.970 line:80%
"A face that charms,
a soul like orchids."

00:02:58.970 --> 00:03:00.900 line:80%
"So bold and bright,
all blooms are swayed."

00:03:00.900 --> 00:03:02.340 line:80%
Poetry on the spot.

00:03:03.300 --> 00:03:04.370 line:80%
What a talent.

00:03:14.210 --> 00:03:15.650 line:80%
I'm from Xuanwu Altar.

00:03:15.650 --> 00:03:17.060 line:80%
I don't know much.

00:03:17.060 --> 00:03:19.020 line:80%
All need your guidance, Mr. Mu.

00:03:19.020 --> 00:03:19.860 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:03:19.860 --> 00:03:21.140 line:80%
Your robe is wrinkled.

00:03:21.140 --> 00:03:22.090 line:80%
Let me take it back.

00:03:22.090 --> 00:03:23.900 line:80%
I'll iron it with heated blue stone.

00:03:25.410 --> 00:03:27.140 line:80%
Dutiful and virtuous.

00:03:27.740 --> 00:03:30.300 line:80%
This fabric is amazing.

00:03:35.580 --> 00:03:36.580 line:80%
Take them all.

00:03:37.690 --> 00:03:38.580 line:80%
All of them?

00:03:40.490 --> 00:03:41.370 line:80%
Mr. Mu.

00:03:41.370 --> 00:03:42.460 line:80%
Elder Yan said

00:03:42.460 --> 00:03:44.690 line:80%
you can only pick one.

00:03:44.690 --> 00:03:45.530 line:80%
One?

00:03:49.410 --> 00:03:50.250 line:80%
Fine.

00:03:50.810 --> 00:03:51.900 line:80%
Then I choose Xing.

00:03:54.020 --> 00:03:54.900 line:80%
Come on, leave now.

00:03:55.090 --> 00:03:55.930 line:80%
Hurry, leave!

00:03:56.180 --> 00:03:57.650 line:80%
Mr. Mu doesn't need servants anymore.

00:04:01.270 --> 00:04:02.180 line:80%
One.

00:04:02.180 --> 00:04:03.810 line:80%
Zhao, tell us.

00:04:03.810 --> 00:04:04.780 line:80%
What's the demon sect like?

00:04:04.780 --> 00:04:05.620 line:80%
Zhao.

00:04:05.620 --> 00:04:07.370 line:80%
Do they really

00:04:07.370 --> 00:04:08.810 line:80%
eat raw meat and drink blood daily?

00:04:08.820 --> 00:04:09.740 line:80%
- Three.
- Yeah.

00:04:09.740 --> 00:04:10.580 line:80%
Yes.

00:04:10.740 --> 00:04:11.780 line:80%
They're much like us.

00:04:12.160 --> 00:04:13.180 line:80%
- Work at sunrise.
- One.

00:04:13.180 --> 00:04:14.370 line:80%
Rest at sunset.

00:04:14.900 --> 00:04:17.170 line:80%
After harvest,
they trade at the marketplace.

00:04:17.170 --> 00:04:18.290 line:80%
They're just ordinary folk.

00:04:18.500 --> 00:04:19.340 line:80%
Just like us?

00:04:22.290 --> 00:04:23.170 line:80%
These ordinary folk

00:04:23.170 --> 00:04:24.940 line:80%
killed tens of thousands of
our Six Sects' disciples.

00:04:25.210 --> 00:04:26.380 line:80%
Their hands are stained red.

00:04:26.970 --> 00:04:29.580 line:80%
Nie Zhe and Mu Qingyan
are ruthless monsters.

00:04:29.580 --> 00:04:31.090 line:80%
They should've died together long ago.

00:04:31.090 --> 00:04:32.500 line:80%
That's too harsh..

00:04:32.500 --> 00:04:33.820 line:80%
Nie Zhe defies all order.

00:04:33.820 --> 00:04:35.410 line:80%
He deserves death for human trials.

00:04:36.650 --> 00:04:38.140 line:80%
But not everyone in the demon sect

00:04:38.940 --> 00:04:40.170 line:80%
is deserving of such condemnation.

00:04:40.170 --> 00:04:41.010 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:41.290 --> 00:04:42.850 line:80%
why are you defending those devils?

00:04:42.850 --> 00:04:43.970 line:80%
Forgot how your aunt, Ms. Cai,

00:04:43.970 --> 00:04:45.210 line:80%
died?

00:04:45.210 --> 00:04:47.020 line:80%
How the Chang clan was wiped out?

00:04:47.020 --> 00:04:48.530 line:80%
You go out to gather some news

00:04:48.530 --> 00:04:50.410 line:80%
and come back forgetting
you're a Six Sects disciple.

00:04:54.410 --> 00:04:55.250 line:80%
I just think

00:04:55.610 --> 00:04:57.090 line:80%
good and evil aren't black and white.

00:04:57.090 --> 00:04:59.340 line:80%
Not all demon sect members are evil.

00:04:59.530 --> 00:05:00.370 line:80%
Likewise,

00:05:00.900 --> 00:05:03.210 line:80%
the Six Sects have
their share of scoundrels too.

00:05:11.100 --> 00:05:14.540 line:80%
(Zhuo)

00:05:30.900 --> 00:05:31.740 line:80%
Milady.

00:05:34.940 --> 00:05:36.460 line:80%
What's wrong?

00:05:36.460 --> 00:05:38.730 line:80%
You were fine when you left.

00:05:39.290 --> 00:05:40.970 line:80%
I want wontons.

00:05:42.380 --> 00:05:43.960 line:80%
Milady, didn't you say

00:05:43.970 --> 00:05:45.410 line:80%
you'd never eat wontons again?

00:05:48.140 --> 00:05:49.290 line:80%
Did I?

00:05:49.780 --> 00:05:50.620 line:80%
Alright.

00:06:02.900 --> 00:06:03.740 line:80%
Zhao.

00:06:08.730 --> 00:06:09.570 line:80%
Zhao.

00:06:12.820 --> 00:06:13.660 line:80%
Master.

00:06:14.020 --> 00:06:15.340 line:80%
I have something to tell you.

00:06:18.820 --> 00:06:19.660 line:80%
Come.

00:06:20.050 --> 00:06:20.890 line:80%
Sit down.

00:06:24.050 --> 00:06:26.580 line:80%
This time,
coming back from the Hanhai Mountains,

00:06:27.410 --> 00:06:29.580 line:80%
do you feel that
not everyone in the demon sect

00:06:29.580 --> 00:06:31.730 line:80%
is a monster?

00:06:32.170 --> 00:06:34.020 line:80%
Some might even be good at heart.

00:06:37.610 --> 00:06:38.970 line:80%
Remember when you were little,

00:06:39.940 --> 00:06:41.580 line:80%
the story Pingshu told you

00:06:41.580 --> 00:06:42.900 line:80%
about the skin-painted demon?

00:06:43.650 --> 00:06:44.490 line:80%
I remember that.

00:06:45.090 --> 00:06:46.050 line:80%
My aunt once said

00:06:47.900 --> 00:06:48.900 line:80%
the skin-painted demon

00:06:49.340 --> 00:06:50.850 line:80%
is a creature with a twisted face,

00:06:50.850 --> 00:06:52.610 line:80%
a bloodthirsty being without restraint.

00:06:53.870 --> 00:06:55.340 line:80%
It eats live human hearts and livers,

00:06:56.020 --> 00:06:57.700 line:80%
uses human skin to deceive people.

00:06:58.050 --> 00:06:59.610 line:80%
A skin-painted demon,
wearing human skin,

00:07:00.380 --> 00:07:01.610 line:80%
looks just like anyone else.

00:07:02.520 --> 00:07:03.680 line:80%
And they can seem even more

00:07:03.900 --> 00:07:05.290 line:80%
understanding

00:07:05.420 --> 00:07:06.580 line:80%
and caring
than real people.

00:07:23.090 --> 00:07:25.090 line:80%
Before showing its bleeding fangs,

00:07:26.850 --> 00:07:28.820 line:80%
it will watch operas with you,

00:07:28.820 --> 00:07:29.660 line:80%
taste wine,

00:07:30.410 --> 00:07:31.970 line:80%
chat and laugh by your side,

00:07:31.970 --> 00:07:34.530 line:80%
even wait two hours
outside Yipin Pavilion

00:07:34.530 --> 00:07:36.580 line:80%
just to buy a fresh roasted pigeon

00:07:36.580 --> 00:07:37.650 line:80%
to satisfy your craving.

00:07:55.580 --> 00:07:57.290 line:80%
But a demon is a demon.

00:07:57.820 --> 00:07:58.660 line:80%
It's a demon.

00:07:59.050 --> 00:08:00.210 line:80%
It feeds on human flesh

00:08:00.610 --> 00:08:01.730 line:80%
and drinks human blood.

00:08:06.410 --> 00:08:07.820 line:80%
Can you imagine it?

00:08:08.340 --> 00:08:09.780 line:80%
Your dearest friend...

00:08:09.780 --> 00:08:10.620 line:80%
I'm here.

00:08:10.900 --> 00:08:12.530 line:80%
Killed by the skin-painted demon,

00:08:13.850 --> 00:08:15.500 line:80%
dying with eyes wide open.

00:08:25.820 --> 00:08:26.660 line:80%
Master.

00:08:27.340 --> 00:08:28.610 line:80%
Jianghu is treacherous.

00:08:29.140 --> 00:08:30.460 line:80%
It's far more cruel

00:08:31.140 --> 00:08:32.380 line:80%
than you think.

00:08:34.020 --> 00:08:35.170 line:80%
Don't make your aunt

00:08:36.780 --> 00:08:37.740 line:80%
worry about you.

00:08:42.170 --> 00:08:43.010 line:80%
Aunt.

00:08:45.530 --> 00:08:47.100 line:80%
Is the skin-painted demon

00:08:47.900 --> 00:08:48.740 line:80%
Master talked about

00:08:48.740 --> 00:08:50.900 line:80%
the masked guy who went to
Snow Mountain with aunt?

00:08:53.380 --> 00:08:54.220 line:80%
Zhao.

00:08:55.220 --> 00:08:56.330 line:80%
You've always been obedient.

00:08:56.650 --> 00:08:57.780 line:80%
You must remember

00:08:57.780 --> 00:08:59.020 line:80%
what Master said.

00:09:00.020 --> 00:09:00.860 line:80%
A demon

00:09:01.980 --> 00:09:03.740 line:80%
always eats people.

00:09:15.290 --> 00:09:16.130 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:09:17.650 --> 00:09:19.410 line:80%
do you know the skin-painted demon?

00:09:21.020 --> 00:09:22.140 line:80%
The skin-painted demon…

00:09:23.020 --> 00:09:24.690 line:80%
I don't know who he is,

00:09:25.450 --> 00:09:26.410 line:80%
but I do know of him.

00:09:26.640 --> 00:09:27.580 line:80%
Were the skin-painted demon

00:09:28.100 --> 00:09:29.410 line:80%
and my aunt

00:09:30.140 --> 00:09:31.290 line:80%
definitely close?

00:09:31.810 --> 00:09:32.810 line:80%
Your aunt

00:09:32.810 --> 00:09:34.410 line:80%
never mentioned his name,

00:09:35.740 --> 00:09:37.900 line:80%
but one year
she asked Granny Needle Zhuo

00:09:37.900 --> 00:09:39.220 line:80%
to embroider a wrist guard.

00:09:40.780 --> 00:09:42.290 line:80%
From its size,

00:09:43.330 --> 00:09:44.780 line:80%
it was for a man.

00:09:45.500 --> 00:09:47.500 line:80%
But isn't Uncle Zhou doing well?

00:09:47.500 --> 00:09:48.410 line:80%
Yes, he is.

00:09:49.050 --> 00:09:50.290 line:80%
But they

00:09:50.290 --> 00:09:51.410 line:80%
can't make it work.

00:09:52.650 --> 00:09:54.450 line:80%
To be honest,

00:09:54.450 --> 00:09:55.500 line:80%
Uncle Zhou's character,

00:09:55.500 --> 00:09:57.100 line:80%
talents and family background

00:09:57.100 --> 00:09:58.170 line:80%
are great.

00:09:58.170 --> 00:10:00.020 line:80%
He and your aunt
were childhood sweethearts,

00:10:00.930 --> 00:10:01.780 line:80%
but

00:10:02.380 --> 00:10:04.100 line:80%
he never truly understood what Pingshu

00:10:04.100 --> 00:10:05.620 line:80%
wanted for her life.

00:10:06.330 --> 00:10:08.410 line:80%
He's gentle and compromising.

00:10:08.410 --> 00:10:09.570 line:80%
And when faced with injustice,

00:10:09.950 --> 00:10:11.050 line:80%
he endured and lets it pass.

00:10:11.530 --> 00:10:12.740 line:80%
Then he hoped others

00:10:13.780 --> 00:10:15.530 line:80%
would also take a step back
and find peace.

00:10:19.170 --> 00:10:21.690 line:80%
My aunt isn't one to swallow her anger.

00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:24.620 line:80%
She's like clear wind and blazing fire.

00:10:25.220 --> 00:10:26.620 line:80%
Clear wind caresses the mountains.

00:10:27.410 --> 00:10:28.860 line:80%
Blazing fire burns all demons.

00:10:32.620 --> 00:10:33.460 line:80%
Master.

00:10:35.020 --> 00:10:35.900 line:80%
Those words

00:10:36.320 --> 00:10:37.780 line:80%
were actually spoken by your Master.

00:10:39.170 --> 00:10:41.500 line:80%
My Master would say something like that?

00:10:41.500 --> 00:10:42.930 line:80%
Lord seems dull,
but he's brilliant within.

00:10:44.650 --> 00:10:45.980 line:80%
After the Righteous-Demonic War,

00:10:47.120 --> 00:10:48.530 line:80%
the Six Sects suffered heavy losses.

00:10:49.020 --> 00:10:50.780 line:80%
Yet within a short span of time,

00:10:50.780 --> 00:10:51.930 line:80%
your Master steadied the Six Sects

00:10:51.930 --> 00:10:53.100 line:80%
and intimidated the demon sect,

00:10:54.100 --> 00:10:55.980 line:80%
bringing peace to Jianghu
for over ten years.

00:10:55.980 --> 00:10:57.570 line:80%
What great strategy.

00:11:02.530 --> 00:11:04.650 line:80%
He brought up that story out of nowhere.

00:11:06.050 --> 00:11:07.690 line:80%
Is it because of Chang Ning?

00:11:13.860 --> 00:11:15.330 line:80%
How's the poison in his body?

00:11:16.020 --> 00:11:17.410 line:80%
Uncle's medicine

00:11:18.410 --> 00:11:19.690 line:80%
suppressed it temporarily.

00:11:20.220 --> 00:11:21.060 line:80%
He won't die.

00:11:21.810 --> 00:11:22.650 line:80%
Temporary suppression

00:11:23.860 --> 00:11:25.050 line:80%
means it'll come back.

00:11:27.410 --> 00:11:28.650 line:80%
From now on,

00:11:30.050 --> 00:11:31.380 line:80%
Zhao, you truly can let him go?

00:11:34.650 --> 00:11:35.860 line:80%
Pretend he never existed.

00:11:44.530 --> 00:11:45.370 line:80%
This time,

00:11:46.100 --> 00:11:47.330 line:80%
listen to your Master.

00:11:48.780 --> 00:11:49.740 line:80%
Fate

00:11:50.140 --> 00:11:51.170 line:80%
can't be forced.

00:11:51.900 --> 00:11:52.900 line:80%
Let it go when it's gone.

00:12:06.170 --> 00:12:08.020 line:80%
I'll go get a new one from Xingjia.

00:12:22.330 --> 00:12:23.240 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:12:23.250 --> 00:12:24.650 line:80%
don't be reckless!

00:12:25.780 --> 00:12:27.690 line:80%
The matter between Mr. Mu and Miss Cai

00:12:27.690 --> 00:12:29.780 line:80%
has unsettled the Li Sect.

00:12:29.780 --> 00:12:30.620 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:12:30.620 --> 00:12:32.450 line:80%
to hold the Chief's seat firmly,

00:12:32.450 --> 00:12:34.140 line:80%
you must marry a sect member

00:12:34.140 --> 00:12:35.450 line:80%
and have children

00:12:35.450 --> 00:12:37.690 line:80%
to stabilize people's hearts.

00:12:37.690 --> 00:12:39.500 line:80%
I think even the village chief's boar

00:12:39.500 --> 00:12:40.930 line:80%
could do that too.

00:12:40.930 --> 00:12:42.220 line:80%
Elder Yan, Why don't you

00:12:42.220 --> 00:12:43.620 line:80%
ask it to be Chief?

00:12:44.780 --> 00:12:46.050 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:12:46.050 --> 00:12:48.430 line:80%
are you still hung up on that Cai girl?

00:12:48.430 --> 00:12:49.290 line:80%
Not only

00:12:49.290 --> 00:12:51.020 line:80%
is she Cai Pingshu's niece,

00:12:51.180 --> 00:12:52.570 line:80%
but the Li Sect and Six Sects

00:12:52.570 --> 00:12:53.980 line:80%
have a 200-year-long blood feud.

00:12:53.980 --> 00:12:55.330 line:80%
Irreconcilable!

00:12:55.330 --> 00:12:56.410 line:80%
Remember

00:12:56.410 --> 00:12:59.050 line:80%
what happened to

00:12:59.050 --> 00:13:00.450 line:80%
the powerful
Chief Mu Donglie in the end?

00:13:01.380 --> 00:13:02.220 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:13:02.570 --> 00:13:04.170 line:80%
do you not remember it?

00:13:05.020 --> 00:13:06.100 line:80%
Mr. Mu, you…

00:13:07.330 --> 00:13:08.170 line:80%
Elder Yan, Elder Yan.

00:13:08.450 --> 00:13:09.290 line:80%
I just remembered

00:13:09.420 --> 00:13:10.740 line:80%
Shangguan got a jar of fine wine.

00:13:10.740 --> 00:13:12.450 line:80%
Let's go drink it all now.

00:13:12.450 --> 00:13:13.690 line:80%
– Let's go, drink.
– Mr. Mu.

00:13:13.690 --> 00:13:14.570 line:80%
I haven't finished.

00:13:14.570 --> 00:13:15.690 line:80%
Go, go, go.

00:13:16.530 --> 00:13:18.170 line:80%
Drink, Elder Yan.

00:13:18.170 --> 00:13:19.930 line:80%
- Come on.
- Why drink? Stop pushing.

00:13:20.690 --> 00:13:21.860 line:80%
- Let me go.
- Elder Yan.

00:13:21.860 --> 00:13:23.500 line:80%
For the grand future of Li Sect, I'll...

00:13:23.500 --> 00:13:24.380 line:80%
Elder Yan.

00:13:25.100 --> 00:13:26.930 line:80%
You really hit a nerve this time.

00:13:27.810 --> 00:13:29.050 line:80%
Miss Cai and the Young Master

00:13:29.050 --> 00:13:31.380 line:80%
are like the Cowboy and Weaver stars
in the sky now.

00:13:31.380 --> 00:13:33.330 line:80%
Separated by the celestial river,
each in sorrow.

00:13:34.050 --> 00:13:35.900 line:80%
Why do you have to hurt him?

00:13:37.100 --> 00:13:38.170 line:80%
Miss Cai

00:13:38.930 --> 00:13:40.500 line:80%
is probably hiding somewhere crying.

00:13:54.170 --> 00:13:55.170 line:80%
So many.

00:13:55.170 --> 00:13:56.170 line:80%
All for me?

00:13:57.690 --> 00:13:58.740 line:80%
Yuzhi said

00:13:58.740 --> 00:14:00.690 line:80%
thanks to you
finding the hot spring stone.

00:14:00.690 --> 00:14:01.530 line:80%
These small gifts

00:14:01.530 --> 00:14:03.740 line:80%
hardly express Uncle Song's gratitude.

00:14:03.740 --> 00:14:04.750 line:80%
Even ten times as much

00:14:04.750 --> 00:14:05.740 line:80%
would still be only fitting.

00:14:07.140 --> 00:14:07.980 line:80%
Indeed.

00:14:10.020 --> 00:14:11.140 line:80%
Yuzhi's inner power

00:14:11.140 --> 00:14:12.450 line:80%
has recovered seventy to eighty percent.

00:14:12.740 --> 00:14:13.580 line:80%
Unfortunately,

00:14:13.860 --> 00:14:15.140 line:80%
there's still some cold energy

00:14:15.140 --> 00:14:16.570 line:80%
in his dantian.

00:14:16.570 --> 00:14:17.570 line:80%
Hard to fully purge.

00:14:18.380 --> 00:14:20.620 line:80%
I'll definitely find the Jade Sunflower
for Yuzhi

00:14:21.100 --> 00:14:23.020 line:80%
to remove the remaining cold energy.

00:14:23.020 --> 00:14:23.860 line:80%
Father, don't worry.

00:14:24.170 --> 00:14:25.020 line:80%
Alright.

00:14:25.020 --> 00:14:25.860 line:80%
I don't worry.

00:14:26.780 --> 00:14:27.620 line:80%
Zhao,

00:14:28.020 --> 00:14:29.170 line:80%
you're young,

00:14:29.170 --> 00:14:30.410 line:80%
yet brave and sharp.

00:14:30.410 --> 00:14:31.740 line:80%
Truly worthy of being Pingshu's niece.

00:14:32.860 --> 00:14:33.980 line:80%
If only
you'd been betrothed

00:14:33.980 --> 00:14:35.020 line:80%
to Yuzhi, that'd be great.

00:14:35.020 --> 00:14:35.860 line:80%
Father.

00:14:36.170 --> 00:14:37.010 line:80%
I... I...

00:14:37.330 --> 00:14:38.980 line:80%
We should thank Zhao

00:14:39.690 --> 00:14:41.690 line:80%
for finding the stone to heal my cousin.

00:14:48.500 --> 00:14:49.410 line:80%
Zhao.

00:14:49.410 --> 00:14:51.410 line:80%
Here's nourishing soup
made by Nanny Mao.

00:14:51.410 --> 00:14:52.690 line:80%
You just returned from your travels.

00:14:52.690 --> 00:14:53.620 line:80%
Need to recharge.

00:14:54.170 --> 00:14:55.010 line:80%
Thank you, Lingbo.

00:15:12.100 --> 00:15:12.940 line:80%
Dear.

00:15:15.530 --> 00:15:16.530 line:80%
Dear, today,

00:15:17.530 --> 00:15:19.170 line:80%
why didn't you go pray?

00:15:19.170 --> 00:15:21.140 line:80%
I copied a scripture for you
in the temple.

00:15:21.820 --> 00:15:23.780 line:80%
Reading it can calm the mind
and ease the spirit.

00:15:23.780 --> 00:15:24.740 line:80%
It will aid your cultivation.

00:15:25.690 --> 00:15:26.620 line:80%
Thank you, Dear.

00:15:28.810 --> 00:15:30.050 line:80%
I heard from Shijun

00:15:30.810 --> 00:15:33.170 line:80%
that Yuzhi's inner power
has mostly returned.

00:15:33.170 --> 00:15:34.020 line:80%
So

00:15:34.020 --> 00:15:35.570 line:80%
why not double the joy?

00:15:35.570 --> 00:15:36.860 line:80%
With him here,

00:15:36.860 --> 00:15:37.860 line:80%
let's fix the kids' wedding

00:15:37.860 --> 00:15:39.620 line:80%
in the next few days.

00:15:41.170 --> 00:15:42.170 line:80%
Dear,

00:15:42.170 --> 00:15:43.220 line:80%
Nie Zhe has gone missing.

00:15:43.220 --> 00:15:44.380 line:80%
The demon sect has a new leader.

00:15:44.380 --> 00:15:45.860 line:80%
We don't know what the new Chief

00:15:45.860 --> 00:15:47.380 line:80%
thinks of the Six Sects,

00:15:47.860 --> 00:15:49.620 line:80%
or if he has any plans.

00:15:50.020 --> 00:15:52.050 line:80%
This may not be the best time.

00:15:52.780 --> 00:15:53.620 line:80%
Besides,

00:15:54.330 --> 00:15:55.570 line:80%
are Yuzhi and Lingbo

00:15:56.170 --> 00:15:57.650 line:80%
truly a good match?

00:15:57.650 --> 00:15:58.980 line:80%
Marriage

00:15:58.980 --> 00:16:00.740 line:80%
is decided by elders.

00:16:00.740 --> 00:16:02.330 line:80%
If we think they suit each other,

00:16:02.330 --> 00:16:03.810 line:80%
then they must be well matched.

00:16:04.810 --> 00:16:06.100 line:80%
As parents,

00:16:06.100 --> 00:16:08.290 line:80%
who wouldn't wish the best
for their children?

00:16:20.690 --> 00:16:21.530 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:16:24.330 --> 00:16:25.170 line:80%
where are you going?

00:16:25.780 --> 00:16:26.980 line:80%
I'm just in the way here.

00:16:27.540 --> 00:16:29.530 line:80%
Guess I'll go down
and carve out my own path.

00:16:30.020 --> 00:16:30.860 line:80%
Save

00:16:31.100 --> 00:16:31.980 line:80%
everyone the trouble.

00:16:32.410 --> 00:16:33.980 line:80%
The demon sect just finished infighting.

00:16:34.220 --> 00:16:35.380 line:80%
The situation is unclear.

00:16:35.640 --> 00:16:37.220 line:80%
Going down the mountain now
is too risky.

00:16:37.530 --> 00:16:39.450 line:80%
Why can Cai Zhao go down to find saliva

00:16:39.690 --> 00:16:40.620 line:80%
and rare stones,

00:16:40.620 --> 00:16:41.460 line:80%
but I can't?

00:16:41.980 --> 00:16:42.820 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:16:43.830 --> 00:16:44.900 line:80%
why compare yourself to her?

00:16:45.220 --> 00:16:47.050 line:80%
Do you think
I'm not as good as Cai Zhao?

00:16:47.530 --> 00:16:48.620 line:80%
Are you like Father

00:16:48.620 --> 00:16:49.900 line:80%
and cousin,

00:16:49.900 --> 00:16:50.930 line:80%
thinking she's the best?

00:16:50.930 --> 00:16:51.810 line:80%
In my heart,

00:16:51.810 --> 00:16:52.780 line:80%
you're the best.

00:16:52.780 --> 00:16:54.140 line:80%
Ten Cai Zhaos can't compare to you.

00:16:57.050 --> 00:16:57.890 line:80%
Cut the sweet talk.

00:16:58.450 --> 00:16:59.410 line:80%
I'm not a child anymore.

00:17:00.740 --> 00:17:01.580 line:80%
I know.

00:17:02.530 --> 00:17:03.890 line:80%
Lingbo, you have your own thoughts.

00:17:05.370 --> 00:17:06.570 line:80%
I won't stop you by force.

00:17:07.180 --> 00:17:08.660 line:80%
But if you want to leave the mountain,

00:17:08.660 --> 00:17:10.090 line:80%
you must first tell Master and Lady Yin.

00:17:10.850 --> 00:17:11.810 line:80%
I'll go with you.

00:17:12.610 --> 00:17:13.460 line:80%
Let's go together.

00:17:35.660 --> 00:17:36.500 line:80%
So

00:17:36.500 --> 00:17:38.370 line:80%
Lingbo plans to leave the mountain,

00:17:38.370 --> 00:17:39.890 line:80%
and it's because of Zhao.

00:17:40.180 --> 00:17:41.740 line:80%
Zhao first saved our sect,

00:17:42.020 --> 00:17:43.980 line:80%
then found a rare stone to heal Yuzhi.

00:17:44.420 --> 00:17:46.370 line:80%
No wonder Yuzhi was moved by her.

00:17:47.290 --> 00:17:48.220 line:80%
But I remember

00:17:48.740 --> 00:17:50.500 line:80%
Zhao already has a fiancé.

00:17:52.500 --> 00:17:53.810 line:80%
Why speak such plain truths aloud?

00:17:54.810 --> 00:17:56.370 line:80%
Don't stir more trouble in the sect.

00:17:59.850 --> 00:18:00.810 line:80%
Yuzhi.

00:18:00.810 --> 00:18:02.460 line:80%
Knew you two tried to elope.

00:18:02.460 --> 00:18:03.300 line:80%
Still not admitting it.

00:18:03.310 --> 00:18:05.220 line:80%
The whole sect's talking about it.

00:18:05.220 --> 00:18:07.130 line:80%
They said you and Zhao failed to elope

00:18:07.130 --> 00:18:08.330 line:80%
and were forced to come back.

00:18:08.330 --> 00:18:09.940 line:80%
Lingbo was so mad
she almost jumped off a cliff.

00:18:09.940 --> 00:18:11.220 line:80%
Luckily, Fengchi stopped her.

00:18:11.700 --> 00:18:12.660 line:80%
But

00:18:12.660 --> 00:18:14.330 line:80%
Yuzhi, don't let it
trouble you too much.

00:18:15.090 --> 00:18:16.660 line:80%
I think Lingbo

00:18:16.660 --> 00:18:18.090 line:80%
was just venting her temper.

00:18:18.090 --> 00:18:19.980 line:80%
If she truly wanted to end her life,

00:18:19.980 --> 00:18:21.420 line:80%
how could she be stopped so easily?

00:18:21.780 --> 00:18:22.780 line:80%
Besides,

00:18:22.780 --> 00:18:24.020 line:80%
Fengchi follows Lingbo

00:18:24.020 --> 00:18:25.460 line:80%
everywhere.

00:18:25.460 --> 00:18:27.460 line:80%
Everyone in Qingque Sect
knows how he feels.

00:18:28.050 --> 00:18:29.780 line:80%
This is the perfect time to tell Master.

00:18:29.880 --> 00:18:30.850 line:80%
Happy ending for everyone!

00:18:31.850 --> 00:18:33.610 line:80%
I think you and Zhao

00:18:33.610 --> 00:18:35.500 line:80%
are a perfect match.

00:18:35.500 --> 00:18:36.420 line:80%
Made for each other.

00:18:36.850 --> 00:18:37.810 line:80%
This time, you...

00:18:37.810 --> 00:18:39.090 line:80%
These absurd rumors

00:18:39.090 --> 00:18:40.290 line:80%
are bad for Zhao,

00:18:40.290 --> 00:18:41.570 line:80%
Fengchi

00:18:41.570 --> 00:18:42.420 line:80%
and Lingbo.

00:18:42.810 --> 00:18:44.460 line:80%
Looks like the whole sect

00:18:44.460 --> 00:18:45.300 line:80%
needs some discipline.

00:18:46.020 --> 00:18:47.570 line:80%
What's the big deal?

00:18:47.570 --> 00:18:49.130 line:80%
We all think you two make a fine pair.

00:18:49.420 --> 00:18:50.260 line:80%
Xingjia.

00:18:52.530 --> 00:18:53.460 line:80%
As for my marriage.

00:18:53.720 --> 00:18:55.570 line:80%
There's no need for the whole sect
to worry about it.

00:18:55.810 --> 00:18:57.050 line:80%
Zhao, why are you...

00:18:57.570 --> 00:18:58.410 line:80%
here?

00:18:58.700 --> 00:19:00.130 line:80%
Yuzhi and I are just pure friends.

00:19:00.130 --> 00:19:01.130 line:80%
We stay within bounds.

00:19:01.570 --> 00:19:03.370 line:80%
How could such nonsense about eloping

00:19:03.370 --> 00:19:04.940 line:80%
spread to sully our reputations?

00:19:05.790 --> 00:19:06.780 line:80%
Xingjia, it's fine you don't

00:19:06.780 --> 00:19:08.700 line:80%
investigate where the rumors started.

00:19:08.700 --> 00:19:10.940 line:80%
But you actually join in
with this nonsense.

00:19:10.940 --> 00:19:12.090 line:80%
It's unbearable.

00:19:12.090 --> 00:19:13.180 line:80%
Zh... Zhao.

00:19:13.530 --> 00:19:15.220 line:80%
I misspoke.

00:19:15.220 --> 00:19:16.220 line:80%
Don't be mad.

00:19:16.550 --> 00:19:17.890 line:80%
Rumors with no basis

00:19:18.130 --> 00:19:19.330 line:80%
always die down.

00:19:19.660 --> 00:19:20.850 line:80%
I'm afraid the rumors

00:19:20.850 --> 00:19:22.020 line:80%
are getting out of hand.

00:19:24.820 --> 00:19:25.660 line:80%
I heard

00:19:25.660 --> 00:19:27.460 line:80%
Yuzhi and Cai Zhao eloped together.

00:19:27.460 --> 00:19:28.300 line:80%
Is that true?

00:19:28.560 --> 00:19:30.420 line:80%
I also heard
she took on the demon sect alone,

00:19:30.420 --> 00:19:32.020 line:80%
no less than Ms. Cai back in her prime.

00:19:32.020 --> 00:19:33.660 line:80%
No wonder Yuzhi admires her.

00:19:35.890 --> 00:19:37.220 line:80%
Who? Who struck me from behind?

00:19:37.220 --> 00:19:38.940 line:80%
Early in the morning, you gossipers

00:19:38.940 --> 00:19:40.130 line:80%
are jabbering nonsense

00:19:40.130 --> 00:19:40.970 line:80%
and stirring up trouble.

00:19:41.530 --> 00:19:42.530 line:80%
How about I see

00:19:42.530 --> 00:19:44.050 line:80%
how your morning training's
coming along?

00:19:44.290 --> 00:19:45.500 line:80%
No, wait.

00:19:45.500 --> 00:19:46.460 line:80%
Cai Zhao, what are you doing?

00:19:47.130 --> 00:19:48.780 line:80%
Zhao just joined the Qingque Sect,

00:19:48.780 --> 00:19:50.660 line:80%
yet you already
exposed the demon sect's disguise.

00:19:50.660 --> 00:19:53.130 line:80%
Then spied on them
for half a month to gather intel.

00:19:53.130 --> 00:19:54.500 line:80%
Truly heroic.

00:19:55.180 --> 00:19:57.180 line:80%
I want to learn from you too.

00:19:57.180 --> 00:19:58.660 line:80%
Enough with the nonsense.

00:20:05.710 --> 00:20:06.570 line:80%
Cai Zhao!

00:20:06.570 --> 00:20:08.370 line:80%
Why use the Sunshine Blade
for a sect duel?

00:20:08.370 --> 00:20:09.810 line:80%
If you've got the skill,
attack together.

00:20:09.810 --> 00:20:10.850 line:80%
If not, stay out of my way.

00:20:10.850 --> 00:20:11.700 line:80%
Cai Zhao!

00:20:11.700 --> 00:20:12.660 line:80%
Don't push us too far!

00:20:13.660 --> 00:20:15.130 line:80%
You asked for this.

00:20:29.610 --> 00:20:31.130 line:80%
Zhao's 36th Form of the Sunshine Blade

00:20:31.130 --> 00:20:32.020 line:80%
are brilliant.

00:20:32.320 --> 00:20:33.370 line:80%
I humbly seek your guidance.

00:20:33.920 --> 00:20:35.130 line:80%
Yuzhi, please make your move.

00:20:39.890 --> 00:20:42.130 line:80%
Yuzhi's using himself as a punching bag

00:20:42.370 --> 00:20:43.940 line:80%
to let Zhao vent.

00:20:46.740 --> 00:20:47.580 line:80%
Zhao.

00:20:50.290 --> 00:20:51.130 line:80%
Yuqi.

00:20:51.320 --> 00:20:52.300 line:80%
Haven't seen you in days.

00:20:52.550 --> 00:20:54.370 line:80%
Zhao, your martial arts
have improved even more.

00:20:57.180 --> 00:20:58.700 line:80%
Congratulations on recovering, Yuzhi.

00:20:59.050 --> 00:21:00.130 line:80%
Yuzhi's skills truly

00:21:00.130 --> 00:21:01.780 line:80%
make you the top of
the Six Sects' new generation.

00:21:02.700 --> 00:21:04.130 line:80%
You flatter me, Young Lord Zhou.

00:21:04.130 --> 00:21:04.980 line:80%
Young Lord Zhou,

00:21:05.610 --> 00:21:07.500 line:80%
your fiancée is about to be taken away.

00:21:07.500 --> 00:21:08.420 line:80%
If I were you,

00:21:08.420 --> 00:21:10.220 line:80%
I'd duel him fair and square.

00:21:10.700 --> 00:21:11.540 line:80%
Utter nonsense.

00:21:11.700 --> 00:21:12.740 line:80%
Who'd buy that?

00:21:13.420 --> 00:21:14.940 line:80%
Fengchi, if you can't talk sense,

00:21:14.940 --> 00:21:17.050 line:80%
better sharpen your martial arts.

00:21:20.940 --> 00:21:21.780 line:80%
You okay?

00:21:23.420 --> 00:21:24.260 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:21:34.920 --> 00:21:36.780 line:80%
Zhou Yuqi's just here to
push for the wedding.

00:21:37.500 --> 00:21:38.780 line:80%
That guy usually

00:21:38.780 --> 00:21:40.330 line:80%
keeps a low profile.

00:21:40.330 --> 00:21:41.460 line:80%
Yet this time, he acted fast.

00:21:42.890 --> 00:21:44.220 line:80%
I told you long ago,

00:21:44.220 --> 00:21:45.850 line:80%
you and Lingbo aren't a good match.

00:21:45.850 --> 00:21:47.220 line:80%
I should've ended
the engagement for you.

00:21:47.220 --> 00:21:49.490 line:80%
Then I wouldn't be this anxious now.

00:21:49.510 --> 00:21:50.370 line:80%
But you

00:21:50.370 --> 00:21:51.980 line:80%
insisted on handling it alone.

00:21:51.980 --> 00:21:53.890 line:80%
You're too stubborn.

00:21:55.740 --> 00:21:56.980 line:80%
If you don't act soon,

00:21:57.370 --> 00:21:59.050 line:80%
Zhao will really marry someone else!

00:21:59.500 --> 00:22:00.370 line:80%
And then?

00:22:00.370 --> 00:22:01.210 line:80%
Then...

00:22:01.610 --> 00:22:03.330 line:80%
Then Zhao'll spend her wedding night

00:22:03.330 --> 00:22:04.570 line:80%
with that Zhou guy.

00:22:04.810 --> 00:22:05.890 line:80%
Red veil lifted.

00:22:06.700 --> 00:22:07.850 line:80%
Candles blown.

00:22:07.850 --> 00:22:09.130 line:80%
You'll regret it soon enough.

00:22:13.550 --> 00:22:15.370 line:80%
After word got out about
you going to the demon Sect,

00:22:16.050 --> 00:22:17.700 line:80%
Mother's been urging me to check on you.

00:22:18.330 --> 00:22:20.220 line:80%
I was worried
you'd be worn out from the trip,

00:22:20.220 --> 00:22:21.060 line:80%
all alone.

00:22:21.460 --> 00:22:22.300 line:80%
Now that I see you again,

00:22:22.700 --> 00:22:23.540 line:80%
you really lost weight.

00:22:24.900 --> 00:22:26.370 line:80%
On the eve of the Righteous-Demonic War,

00:22:26.890 --> 00:22:29.020 line:80%
Lord Zhou actually married Miss Min.

00:22:29.570 --> 00:22:31.050 line:80%
Even if your aunt was busy fighting evil

00:22:31.050 --> 00:22:32.130 line:80%
and never married,

00:22:32.130 --> 00:22:33.780 line:80%
he still jumped the gun, didn't he?

00:22:36.020 --> 00:22:36.980 line:80%
Lately,

00:22:36.980 --> 00:22:38.780 line:80%
I've been sorting through
my aunt's past.

00:22:38.780 --> 00:22:40.330 line:80%
I wonder if your mother, Lady Min,

00:22:40.330 --> 00:22:41.980 line:80%
was acquainted with my aunt.

00:22:41.980 --> 00:22:42.820 line:80%
Whether they ever

00:22:43.530 --> 00:22:45.180 line:80%
traveled somewhere together,

00:22:45.660 --> 00:22:46.980 line:80%
or met anyone special?

00:22:50.810 --> 00:22:52.500 line:80%
My mother has no time to go out.

00:22:53.740 --> 00:22:55.330 line:80%
Father's focused on developing weapons

00:22:55.680 --> 00:22:56.940 line:80%
and barely handles household affairs.

00:22:57.850 --> 00:22:59.050 line:80%
We have grandmother,

00:22:59.570 --> 00:23:00.420 line:80%
aunts,

00:23:00.420 --> 00:23:01.260 line:80%
uncles,

00:23:01.420 --> 00:23:02.740 line:80%
and uncles living under the same roof.

00:23:03.570 --> 00:23:04.940 line:80%
Their daily needs,

00:23:04.940 --> 00:23:06.330 line:80%
marriages, rituals

00:23:06.330 --> 00:23:07.980 line:80%
are all managed by Mother alone.

00:23:07.980 --> 00:23:09.890 line:80%
Whenever there are disputes
among the sisters-in-law,

00:23:09.890 --> 00:23:11.460 line:80%
it is Mother who settles them.

00:23:11.460 --> 00:23:13.090 line:80%
Social visits,

00:23:13.090 --> 00:23:14.460 line:80%
shop inventories,

00:23:14.460 --> 00:23:15.570 line:80%
accounting and petty affairs.

00:23:15.940 --> 00:23:17.290 line:80%
Mother handles it all.

00:23:19.330 --> 00:23:20.530 line:80%
Lady Min is truly capable.

00:23:21.090 --> 00:23:22.290 line:80%
Mother always says

00:23:22.290 --> 00:23:23.740 line:80%
Zhao is even more capable than she is.

00:23:24.180 --> 00:23:25.740 line:80%
Once you marry into Peiqiong Manor,

00:23:26.120 --> 00:23:27.050 line:80%
all this will be yours.

00:23:27.700 --> 00:23:28.660 line:80%
From now on,

00:23:28.660 --> 00:23:30.810 line:80%
you will be
the Manager of Peiqiong Manor.

00:23:32.920 --> 00:23:33.860 line:80%
What's wrong with you?

00:23:35.180 --> 00:23:36.290 line:80%
Your face looks a bit pale.

00:23:37.330 --> 00:23:38.170 line:80%
Tired?

00:23:38.660 --> 00:23:39.810 line:80%
A bit.

00:23:40.850 --> 00:23:42.530 line:80%
Yuqi, this time you came here.

00:23:42.530 --> 00:23:43.460 line:80%
Was it only to open a shop?

00:23:43.890 --> 00:23:45.130 line:80%
I'm here to discuss

00:23:45.460 --> 00:23:46.330 line:80%
our upcoming wedding

00:23:46.780 --> 00:23:48.420 line:80%
with Lord Qi and the elders.

00:24:00.290 --> 00:24:01.130 line:80%
Yuzhi,

00:24:03.320 --> 00:24:04.850 line:80%
has Young Lord Zhou
been properly settled?

00:24:07.220 --> 00:24:08.370 line:80%
Yuzhi, you're here for me?

00:24:10.500 --> 00:24:11.500 line:80%
On this demon sect trip,

00:24:11.850 --> 00:24:13.050 line:80%
as your senior brother,

00:24:13.330 --> 00:24:14.660 line:80%
I failed to protect you.

00:24:16.700 --> 00:24:17.570 line:80%
These handbooks

00:24:17.710 --> 00:24:19.740 line:80%
are Jianghu tales and Six Sects' news
I gathered

00:24:19.740 --> 00:24:20.580 line:80%
over the past half year.

00:24:20.780 --> 00:24:22.180 line:80%
And many demon sect techniques.

00:24:23.290 --> 00:24:24.700 line:80%
They might come in handy next time.

00:24:25.660 --> 00:24:26.610 line:80%
Thank you, Yuzhi.

00:24:31.020 --> 00:24:32.290 line:80%
You seems a bit down.

00:24:37.610 --> 00:24:39.020 line:80%
I just realized

00:24:39.460 --> 00:24:40.740 line:80%
that many things

00:24:41.620 --> 00:24:43.130 line:80%
are hard
to align actions with beliefs.

00:24:44.020 --> 00:24:44.860 line:80%
Zhao,

00:24:46.290 --> 00:24:47.300 line:80%
is this marriage

00:24:48.460 --> 00:24:49.850 line:80%
really what you want?

00:24:50.980 --> 00:24:52.180 line:80%
The Qingque Sect breakthrough.

00:24:52.180 --> 00:24:53.420 line:80%
The Bliss Palace battle.

00:24:53.420 --> 00:24:55.290 line:80%
I knew then
you were an eagle, not a sparrow.

00:24:55.290 --> 00:24:56.700 line:80%
You shouldn't be trapped
in a small space.

00:24:57.290 --> 00:24:58.420 line:80%
If your heart already hesitates,

00:24:58.420 --> 00:25:00.090 line:80%
why not find a better match?

00:25:00.610 --> 00:25:01.660 line:80%
What about you, Yuzhi?

00:25:02.420 --> 00:25:03.570 line:80%
Was your marriage what you wanted?

00:25:14.810 --> 00:25:16.180 line:80%
It's all right, don't worry.

00:25:16.180 --> 00:25:17.810 line:80%
Milady should be back soon.

00:25:17.810 --> 00:25:18.650 line:80%
Xiaolan?

00:25:22.180 --> 00:25:23.500 line:80%
Zhao, you're finally back.

00:25:26.020 --> 00:25:28.130 line:80%
I made all these pastries myself.

00:25:28.780 --> 00:25:31.050 line:80%
In a few days,
I'll return to the Siqi Sect.

00:25:31.500 --> 00:25:32.980 line:80%
So I came to say goodbye.

00:25:33.370 --> 00:25:35.740 line:80%
Thanks for taking care of me
at Qingque Sect.

00:25:35.940 --> 00:25:36.780 line:80%
Xiaolan.

00:25:36.940 --> 00:25:38.090 line:80%
Why are you leaving so soon?

00:25:38.790 --> 00:25:40.090 line:80%
Is something wrong at the Siqi Sect?

00:25:47.050 --> 00:25:48.730 line:80%
Nothing urgent, really.

00:25:49.460 --> 00:25:51.090 line:80%
Father called me back

00:25:51.610 --> 00:25:52.800 line:80%
to arrange a marriage.

00:25:53.180 --> 00:25:54.530 line:80%
You're still so young.

00:25:55.130 --> 00:25:57.480 line:80%
Why is your family rushing marriage?

00:25:57.700 --> 00:25:59.100 line:80%
You may not know this, Zhao.

00:25:59.320 --> 00:26:00.700 line:80%
My father's concubine is in charge.

00:26:01.130 --> 00:26:02.940 line:80%
She sees me as an obstacle in her way.

00:26:02.940 --> 00:26:05.020 line:80%
She's been urging Father
to marry me off early.

00:26:05.220 --> 00:26:06.750 line:80%
But since Lord Yang is your Father,

00:26:07.220 --> 00:26:08.750 line:80%
how can he treat you so unfairly?

00:26:09.090 --> 00:26:10.090 line:80%
How is that biased?

00:26:11.290 --> 00:26:13.960 line:80%
Father said he'd found me
a good husband's family.

00:26:14.420 --> 00:26:15.680 line:80%
As long as I obey him,

00:26:16.020 --> 00:26:17.310 line:80%
I'll live a worry-free life.

00:26:21.850 --> 00:26:23.700 line:80%
But my mother lived like that.

00:26:24.370 --> 00:26:25.210 line:80%
Followed every rule.

00:26:25.980 --> 00:26:27.090 line:80%
Obeyed father before marriage,

00:26:27.090 --> 00:26:28.500 line:80%
her husband after,

00:26:28.500 --> 00:26:29.370 line:80%
living by his word.

00:26:29.370 --> 00:26:30.420 line:80%
Remained faithful.

00:26:31.850 --> 00:26:33.370 line:80%
Yet she compromised all her life

00:26:33.850 --> 00:26:34.740 line:80%
and still met a bad end.

00:26:36.610 --> 00:26:38.180 line:80%
I saw it with my own eyes.

00:26:38.740 --> 00:26:40.160 line:80%
How can I believe

00:26:40.220 --> 00:26:42.340 line:80%
that by following parents' will
and the matchmaker's words,

00:26:42.460 --> 00:26:43.810 line:80%
I would find a perfect marriage?

00:26:44.460 --> 00:26:45.780 line:80%
The world acts like

00:26:46.390 --> 00:26:48.250 line:80%
marriage

00:26:48.520 --> 00:26:50.670 line:80%
is the only important thing for women.

00:26:50.940 --> 00:26:52.150 line:80%
Why can't women have

00:26:52.170 --> 00:26:53.670 line:80%
their own dreams and aspirations?

00:26:54.370 --> 00:26:55.780 line:80%
Ms. Cai made them come true.

00:26:55.780 --> 00:26:57.180 line:80%
Then why, in this world,

00:26:57.180 --> 00:26:58.940 line:80%
can't there be a second, a third,

00:26:58.940 --> 00:27:00.500 line:80%
countless others like Ms. Cai?

00:27:04.020 --> 00:27:05.100 line:80%
Aunt truly lived

00:27:05.570 --> 00:27:06.850 line:80%
a life of justice.

00:27:09.500 --> 00:27:10.780 line:80%
How will you handle it

00:27:11.350 --> 00:27:12.420 line:80%
after returning to Siqi Sect?

00:27:14.930 --> 00:27:17.150 line:80%
I'll try to negotiate with Father.

00:27:18.050 --> 00:27:19.660 line:80%
After all, marriage is a serious matter.

00:27:19.660 --> 00:27:21.560 line:80%
I need to follow my heart.

00:27:22.980 --> 00:27:23.820 line:80%
Zhao,

00:27:24.180 --> 00:27:25.330 line:80%
give your all in everything,

00:27:25.330 --> 00:27:26.370 line:80%
and act from the heart.

00:27:28.700 --> 00:27:30.030 line:80%
My Mother used to say

00:27:30.290 --> 00:27:31.720 line:80%
the hardest thing is to choose.

00:27:32.150 --> 00:27:34.020 line:80%
When faced with a tough decision,

00:27:34.220 --> 00:27:35.290 line:80%
count to ten,

00:27:35.700 --> 00:27:36.810 line:80%
calm down,

00:27:37.330 --> 00:27:39.180 line:80%
and listen to your heart.

00:27:39.810 --> 00:27:40.940 line:80%
Then you'll know what to do.

00:27:44.700 --> 00:27:45.570 line:80%
Zhao.

00:27:45.570 --> 00:27:46.410 line:80%
I'm leaving.

00:27:46.700 --> 00:27:47.570 line:80%
Take care, Xiaolan.

00:28:19.090 --> 00:28:19.930 line:80%
Zhao.

00:28:20.090 --> 00:28:20.930 line:80%
Zhao.

00:28:22.330 --> 00:28:23.460 line:80%
Why are you spacing out?

00:28:23.460 --> 00:28:24.660 line:80%
Get up to collect gifts.

00:28:24.890 --> 00:28:25.730 line:80%
What gifts?

00:28:38.290 --> 00:28:39.130 line:80%
Min.

00:28:39.420 --> 00:28:40.330 line:80%
Zhao.

00:28:41.850 --> 00:28:43.780 line:80%
These were all sent by Yuqi?

00:28:43.780 --> 00:28:44.630 line:80%
No.

00:28:44.640 --> 00:28:45.660 line:80%
They were arranged by Aunt.

00:28:46.330 --> 00:28:47.180 line:80%
After Yuqi left,

00:28:47.180 --> 00:28:49.370 line:80%
Aunt spoke of Yuqi and Zhao's wedding.

00:28:50.290 --> 00:28:51.330 line:80%
Aunt said

00:28:51.330 --> 00:28:52.740 line:80%
you've always had a mind of your own,

00:28:53.290 --> 00:28:54.330 line:80%
so you should check

00:28:54.330 --> 00:28:56.660 line:80%
the betrothal gifts yourself.

00:28:57.050 --> 00:28:58.370 line:80%
If anything's missing,

00:28:58.370 --> 00:28:59.780 line:80%
we can make up for it in time.

00:28:59.780 --> 00:29:00.740 line:80%
So

00:29:00.740 --> 00:29:02.130 line:80%
she sent me to bring them.

00:29:02.570 --> 00:29:03.740 line:80%
What a great husband's family.

00:29:04.130 --> 00:29:04.980 line:80%
Zhao,

00:29:04.980 --> 00:29:06.090 line:80%
you're so lucky.

00:29:08.810 --> 00:29:09.650 line:80%
Min.

00:29:09.890 --> 00:29:10.890 line:80%
Shouldn't my wedding

00:29:11.180 --> 00:29:13.130 line:80%
wait until I finish my training?

00:29:13.660 --> 00:29:15.810 line:80%
Why send the betrothal gifts so early?

00:29:16.940 --> 00:29:18.330 line:80%
Aunt cares for you

00:29:18.980 --> 00:29:21.570 line:80%
and hopes you'll marry soon.

00:29:24.850 --> 00:29:26.660 line:80%
Marriage is a joyful thing.

00:29:26.660 --> 00:29:27.850 line:80%
And my Mother said,

00:29:27.850 --> 00:29:28.940 line:80%
when Zhao weds,

00:29:28.940 --> 00:29:31.020 line:80%
the Qingque Sect must hold
a grand celebration.

00:29:31.220 --> 00:29:33.050 line:80%
Come, let's see the gifts.

00:29:35.050 --> 00:29:36.290 line:80%
This is the Mist Veil Canopy.

00:29:36.290 --> 00:29:37.890 line:80%
Hang it in the room on hot days.

00:29:37.890 --> 00:29:39.330 line:80%
The scent can keep mosquitoes away.

00:29:40.050 --> 00:29:41.810 line:80%
Yuqi has one in his chamber.

00:29:44.090 --> 00:29:45.530 line:80%
This is the Pine-Stone Inkstone.

00:29:45.530 --> 00:29:47.460 line:80%
It's made from cliff iron pine.

00:29:47.460 --> 00:29:48.570 line:80%
The ink smells fresh.

00:29:48.810 --> 00:29:50.570 line:80%
Yuqi loves using it to copy scriptures.

00:29:50.810 --> 00:29:51.650 line:80%
It calms the mind.

00:29:53.030 --> 00:29:54.130 line:80%
This is the Fox Down Garment.

00:29:54.180 --> 00:29:55.850 line:80%
It's made from
the softest down at a fox's neck.

00:29:56.220 --> 00:29:58.530 line:80%
Yuqi wears it
next to his skin in winter.

00:30:01.090 --> 00:30:01.930 line:80%
Wait.

00:30:02.370 --> 00:30:03.740 line:80%
At first, I only thought

00:30:03.740 --> 00:30:06.050 line:80%
Min was just closer to Mr. Mu.

00:30:06.460 --> 00:30:07.530 line:80%
But now it seems

00:30:08.330 --> 00:30:09.570 line:80%
your bond feels rather unusual.

00:30:10.850 --> 00:30:12.460 line:80%
How's a girl supposed to know what her

00:30:12.460 --> 00:30:13.940 line:80%
childhood friend wears underneath?

00:30:14.460 --> 00:30:16.290 line:80%
I don't even know what Yuzhi wears.

00:30:16.570 --> 00:30:17.530 line:80%
That kind of closeness.

00:30:17.530 --> 00:30:18.940 line:80%
Quite out of the ordinary.

00:30:21.850 --> 00:30:22.700 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:30:23.180 --> 00:30:25.180 line:80%
I grew up alongside Yuqi.

00:30:25.570 --> 00:30:26.980 line:80%
Naturally, I know what he likes.

00:30:28.090 --> 00:30:29.330 line:80%
With what you just said,

00:30:29.610 --> 00:30:31.130 line:80%
if someone with ill intent heard it,

00:30:31.600 --> 00:30:33.570 line:80%
who knows
what misunderstandings will arise?

00:30:33.780 --> 00:30:35.810 line:80%
You said it yourself.
How is it my fault?

00:30:36.570 --> 00:30:37.890 line:80%
What's wrong with Peiqiong Manor,

00:30:38.220 --> 00:30:40.130 line:80%
raising someone like you
who twists the truth?

00:30:40.420 --> 00:30:41.260 line:80%
You...

00:30:41.500 --> 00:30:42.340 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:30:42.570 --> 00:30:43.610 line:80%
My bad for talking too much!

00:30:46.020 --> 00:30:47.370 line:80%
Outdated goods.

00:30:58.980 --> 00:30:59.820 line:80%
I'm so furious!

00:31:03.220 --> 00:31:04.180 line:80%
I'm so furious!

00:31:04.180 --> 00:31:05.180 line:80%
That Cai Zhao.

00:31:06.660 --> 00:31:07.500 line:80%
I'm so mad.

00:31:10.460 --> 00:31:11.500 line:80%
Already grown this much,

00:31:11.500 --> 00:31:13.740 line:80%
yet still so reckless and rash.

00:31:13.740 --> 00:31:14.810 line:80%
It's all because Cai Zhao.

00:31:15.370 --> 00:31:17.330 line:80%
I tried to help her
deal with that Zhou clan's sister.

00:31:17.330 --> 00:31:18.170 line:80%
But her?

00:31:18.460 --> 00:31:19.300 line:80%
So ungrateful.

00:31:22.050 --> 00:31:22.980 line:80%
Zhou clan's sister?

00:31:24.330 --> 00:31:25.810 line:80%
Zhou Yuqi has a sister?

00:31:26.050 --> 00:31:27.290 line:80%
It's that Min Xinrou.

00:31:27.940 --> 00:31:29.660 line:80%
Cai Zhao really acts recklessly.

00:31:30.020 --> 00:31:31.570 line:80%
With Min Xinrou around,

00:31:31.780 --> 00:31:32.940 line:80%
she'll be in for trouble.

00:31:34.940 --> 00:31:35.780 line:80%
Mother.

00:31:36.020 --> 00:31:38.290 line:80%
I heard Min Xinrou's

00:31:38.290 --> 00:31:40.370 line:80%
parents died young.
She was raised by the Zhou clan.

00:31:40.740 --> 00:31:42.500 line:80%
And grew up with Zhou Yuqi.

00:31:42.980 --> 00:31:43.820 line:80%
That makes sense.

00:31:44.290 --> 00:31:46.050 line:80%
Their childhood bond

00:31:46.050 --> 00:31:47.420 line:80%
is hard to interfere with by outsiders.

00:31:48.020 --> 00:31:50.020 line:80%
No matter how glorious
Cai Zhao was before,

00:31:50.570 --> 00:31:51.850 line:80%
after marrying into the Zhou clan,

00:31:52.450 --> 00:31:54.150 line:80%
she'll be the mistress on the surface,

00:31:54.330 --> 00:31:55.460 line:80%
but secretly,

00:31:55.460 --> 00:31:56.780 line:80%
who knows what she'll be.

00:31:57.880 --> 00:31:59.180 line:80%
I've told you countless times.

00:31:59.180 --> 00:32:00.370 line:80%
You're a daughter of the Yin clan,

00:32:00.940 --> 00:32:03.090 line:80%
the future Lady of Qingque Sect.

00:32:03.090 --> 00:32:05.810 line:80%
Yet you spend your days
gossiping about others' private matters,

00:32:05.820 --> 00:32:06.980 line:80%
spreading comments and rumors,

00:32:07.360 --> 00:32:08.780 line:80%
aren't you afraid of losing your grace?

00:32:08.980 --> 00:32:09.860 line:80%
Mother,

00:32:09.860 --> 00:32:10.980 line:80%
why are you just like Father,

00:32:11.220 --> 00:32:12.740 line:80%
always speaking up for Cai Zhao?

00:32:12.940 --> 00:32:14.020 line:80%
It's because of you

00:32:14.220 --> 00:32:15.700 line:80%
that she's so reckless.

00:32:20.100 --> 00:32:20.940 line:80%
Mother,

00:32:21.140 --> 00:32:22.780 line:80%
with Cai Zhao's fiery temper,

00:32:22.980 --> 00:32:24.180 line:80%
once she marries into the Zhou clan,

00:32:24.660 --> 00:32:26.300 line:80%
she'll turn the Zhou clan upside down.

00:32:28.980 --> 00:32:30.460 line:80%
That's the least of it.

00:32:31.540 --> 00:32:33.500 line:80%
Their marriage itself
might fall through.

00:32:34.140 --> 00:32:35.980 line:80%
If their marriage really falls through,

00:32:36.380 --> 00:32:38.980 line:80%
Milady's marriage with Mr. Song

00:32:39.330 --> 00:32:41.020 line:80%
is bound to be affected.

00:32:41.460 --> 00:32:42.340 line:80%
No way!

00:32:42.340 --> 00:32:43.500 line:80%
What's yours is destined to be.

00:32:43.500 --> 00:32:44.940 line:80%
No one can take it.

00:32:45.700 --> 00:32:47.180 line:80%
But what's not

00:32:47.500 --> 00:32:49.060 line:80%
can't be forced.

00:32:49.500 --> 00:32:50.340 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:32:50.900 --> 00:32:52.380 line:80%
do you insist on this?

00:33:00.820 --> 00:33:03.380 line:80%
Madam has comforted Milady
several times.

00:33:04.020 --> 00:33:06.460 line:80%
If she really can't let go of Mr. Song,

00:33:06.620 --> 00:33:07.460 line:80%
why not

00:33:08.420 --> 00:33:09.780 line:80%
help her again?

00:33:21.540 --> 00:33:22.380 line:80%
Milady.

00:33:22.780 --> 00:33:24.660 line:80%
These hairpins and rings.

00:33:24.660 --> 00:33:26.330 line:80%
You rarely wear them when training.

00:33:26.590 --> 00:33:28.370 line:80%
It's a waste to keep them locked up.

00:33:28.620 --> 00:33:30.860 line:80%
Take whatever you like.

00:33:31.010 --> 00:33:32.880 line:80%
Thank you, Milady!

00:33:33.620 --> 00:33:35.200 line:80%
And these cloths, silk,

00:33:35.210 --> 00:33:36.610 line:80%
books, and medicinal herbs.

00:33:36.620 --> 00:33:37.460 line:80%
Where should I put them?

00:33:37.660 --> 00:33:38.500 line:80%
Whatever.

00:33:38.740 --> 00:33:39.700 line:80%
Up to you.

00:33:43.980 --> 00:33:44.820 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:33:45.940 --> 00:33:47.700 line:80%
What now, Lingbo?

00:33:48.020 --> 00:33:48.900 line:80%
Want another fight?

00:33:49.460 --> 00:33:50.900 line:80%
You still can't beat me.

00:33:52.580 --> 00:33:53.420 line:80%
Alright.

00:33:54.420 --> 00:33:55.580 line:80%
Everyone says you're clever.

00:33:55.680 --> 00:33:56.940 line:80%
But to me, you seem truly foolish.

00:33:57.220 --> 00:33:58.740 line:80%
Min Xinrou clearly...

00:33:58.740 --> 00:34:00.220 line:80%
She likes Yuqi.

00:34:00.220 --> 00:34:01.100 line:80%
You knew?

00:34:01.780 --> 00:34:03.020 line:80%
I'm not blind.

00:34:03.020 --> 00:34:03.860 line:80%
Then...

00:34:04.100 --> 00:34:05.180 line:80%
You don't mind?

00:34:07.660 --> 00:34:09.540 line:80%
You don't like Zhou Yuqi?

00:34:14.180 --> 00:34:15.020 line:80%
Cai Zhao!

00:34:16.980 --> 00:34:17.820 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:34:18.060 --> 00:34:19.420 line:80%
I hate your

00:34:19.420 --> 00:34:20.740 line:80%
detached attitude the most.

00:34:21.420 --> 00:34:23.300 line:80%
Your fiancé has such a

00:34:23.300 --> 00:34:24.180 line:80%
close female confidante.

00:34:24.460 --> 00:34:26.100 line:80%
Don't tell me
you'd feel nothing in your heart.

00:34:27.180 --> 00:34:29.020 line:80%
What if it were you, Lingbo?

00:34:29.420 --> 00:34:30.300 line:80%
What would you do?

00:34:31.740 --> 00:34:32.780 line:80%
Call off the engagement?

00:34:44.960 --> 00:34:55.620 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:35:14.380 --> 00:35:18.790 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:35:19.355 --> 00:35:23.970 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:35:24.310 --> 00:35:28.875 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:35:29.400 --> 00:35:33.700 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:35:36.645 --> 00:35:41.345 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:35:41.870 --> 00:35:46.160 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:35:46.820 --> 00:35:50.850 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:35:51.165 --> 00:35:56.290 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:35:56.865 --> 00:36:01.675 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:36:01.890 --> 00:36:06.060 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:36:06.785 --> 00:36:10.720 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:36:11.220 --> 00:36:16.495 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:36:39.225 --> 00:36:44.355 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:36:44.720 --> 00:36:49.090 line:80%
